  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <i>Cursed House</i> series offers a more challenging take on Match 3 games, combining traditional mechanics with an engaging puzzle design that demands strategic thinking. Beyond just matching tiles, players must navigate through:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>90 unique Match 3 levels</strong> that come with an interactive hint system to guide you through tougher spots.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 Spot the Difference scenes</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>25 Diamond games</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>15 Solitaire games</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The series also features a <strong>Relaxed or Limited Moves mode</strong> for players seeking even greater challenge, as these modes require careful planning to optimize moves.  </p>",
